      "comment": "MEMORIES OF ROSE (1) produced a moderate effort last time when fifth at Gawler over 531m behind Dakota Rylen (31.60) in a Grade 5. Was a winner the start prior. Can make amends. CORRYONG (2) turned in a plain run last time when fifth at this track over 595m behind Kia Keeping (35.49) in a Grade 6. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. NITROUS (4) was out of in the placings when fifth last time but prior to that clocked a speedy 42.90 win over 730m at this track. Top win two back and can measure up again. CANYA VIVI (3) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
